content: That's really helpful, thanks for the suggestions! I think a spa gift certificate or a cozy robe and slippers would be a great idea for Rachel. By the way, I attended my cousin's baby shower today, and it was amazing to celebrate the upcoming arrival of little Ava. She's already had her baby, a 7lbs 11oz and 20 inches long sweetie, and I got to visit them at the hospital a few days later.
